## Entry 008 — Witness and Horizon: Council Evaluation and Deferred Activation
**Date:** 2026-06-09
**Participants:** Founder, full council (Claude Code session)
**Session type:** Proposal evaluation, amendment, architectural decision

**Proposal evaluated:** `canopy-witness-horizon-proposal-v0.2.md`
Two new agents — The Witness (internal mirror: documented character vs. stated values)
and The Horizon (external mutation engine: signal synthesis, projection frameworks,
mutation proposals) — submitted by the founder for council deliberation.

