### Decision 010.01 — Resolution B: Proceed with Modification. Unanimous.

**What was decided:** All three upgrades are approved in principle. Implementation is blocked on five modifications that must be resolved before the corresponding build phase begins. No code is written until the relevant modification is complete.

**Reasoning:** The brief's diagnosis is accurate and the upgrade is constitutionally motivated. The council found no basis to pause or reject. Two DISSONTs were issued; both have resolution paths. The core direction is sound.

**Vote:** Operator — B. Listener — B. Steward — B. Guardian — B. Inventor — B. Builder — B. Challenger — B. Elder — B.

